  "texts": [
    "Food security has now become a top concern for all countries due to population growth, depletion of natural resources, loss of farmland, and unpredictable environmental conditions.",
    "These challenges are further intensified by the transformation of the agricultural sector into smart agriculture, which utilizes the Internet of Things and big data techniques to enhance productivity and operational effectiveness (Home et al. 2017; Quy et al. 2022).",
    "The studies that were reviewed highlight the significant potential of IoT to revolutionize the sector by improving productivity and resource management (Dhal et al. 2024; Raj et al. 2023).",
    "While other Agritech innovations are also important, IoT stands out for its ability to provide real-time data on weather conditions, soil moisture levels, and pest monitoring.",
    "This enables farmers to make informed decisions that can increase efficiency and promote sustainability."
  ],
